OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FOlivia Dean won big at the 2026 Brit
OL,7,FAwards as she scooped four gongs - as
OL,8,Fa joke about Lord Peter Mandelson and
OL,9,Fa political chants were censored by
OL,10,FITV.
OL,12,FThe channel also removed numerous
OL,13,Finstances of swearing, just a week
OL,14,Fafter controversy at the Bafta Awards
OL,15,Fsaw the BBC broadcast a racial slur
OL,16,Fmade by a member of the audience with
OL,17,FTourette syndrome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
