PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FOne of the notable comments that was
OL,7,Fremoved saw presenter Jack Whitehall
OL,8,Fmake a joke about Lord Mandelson as he
OL,9,Fspoke to a table filled with political
OL,10,Ffigures including Greater Manchester
OL,11,FMayor Andy Burnham and Culture
OL,12,FSecretary Lisa Nandy.
OL,14,FGeese drummer Max Bassin was also
OL,15,Fcensored as he collected the New York
OL,16,Fband's award for best international
OL,17,Fgroup but was censored as he made
OL,18,Fpolitical statements around the Middle
OL,19,FEast and America.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
