OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FSoulful pop star Dean took home awards
OL,7,Ffor artist of the year, album of the
OL,8,Fyear, pop act, and song of the year
OL,9,Ffor Rein Me In, alongside Sam Fender,
OL,10,Fwhose album People Watching the song
OL,11,Ffeatures on.
OL,13,FBecoming emotional after winning album
OL,14,Fof the year for The Art Of Loving, she
OL,15,Fsaid: "Making this album has changed
OL,16,Fmy life, I feel so proud to have made
OL,17,Fit, and to work with everybody that I
OL,18,Fdid on it...
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
