PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,F"Thank you so much for believing in me
OL,7,Fwhen I didn't really believe in myself
OL,8,Fsometimes... this album is just about
OL,9,Flove and loving each other in a world
OL,10,Fthat feels lovelessness right now, so
OL,11,FI don't know, thank you."
OL,13,FAfter receiving song of the year, Dean
OL,14,Fthanked Fender for "a beautiful song",
OL,15,Fadding it had "been a pleasure to be a
OL,16,Fpart of it".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]vD@TOUvD@eO]wD@OOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
