OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FFender said he loved the song, which
OL,7,Fhe had written about four years ago,
OL,8,Fadding: "Olivia made it her own, and I
OL,9,Fjust want to say thank you to Olivia
OL,10,Fand her fans."
OL,12,FWolf Alice used their group of the
OL,13,Fyear winners' speech to call for
OL,14,Fsupport for the UK's small venues.
OL,16,FSinger Ellie Rowsell said: "It's worth
OL,17,Fmentioning that despite the billions
OL,18,Fof pounds the live sector contributes
OL,19,Fto our economy, last year, 30
OL,20,Findependent venues closed down.
OL,26,@pD@IOUrD@NO]xD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
