PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,F"Six thousand jobs were lost, and over
OL,7,Fhalf of small venues reported making
OL,8,Fno profit at all, it shouldn't be a
OL,9,Fbattle to survive as a band or any
OL,10,Fartist.
OL,12,F"We shouldn't be reliant on favours or
OL,13,Fanyone on funding schemes in order to
OL,14,Fdo things at a level we feel proud of.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
