PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,F"It shouldn't feel like a golden
OL,7,Fticket, but a viable career decision
OL,8,Ffor anyone from any background,
OL,9,Fbecause we only have to look around at
OL,10,Feveryone here today, and see how proud
OL,11,Fwe are of Britain's musical
OL,12,Fcontribution.
OL,14,F"And how much money there is to be
OL,15,Fspent to nurture and protect the UK's
OL,16,Famazing music scene."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@UO]
