OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FSpanish singer Rosalia, who was joined
OL,7,Fon stage by Bjork for a performance of
OL,8,FBerghain, took home the award for
OL,9,Finternational act, following a year
OL,10,Fwhich saw her release her critically
OL,11,Facclaimed Lux album.
OL,13,FShe said it was "insane" to win: "I
OL,14,Fwas so grateful just to be here
OL,15,Ftonight, just to perform."
OL,17,FRosalia added: "It's such an honour to
OL,18,Fbring my music far from home, and I
OL,19,Fwould love to share this (award) with
OL,20,Fall my peers who also make music in
OL,21,FSpanish."
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@XO]uD@bOUwD@ZO]yD@POU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
