OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,F"When the outside world can feel
OL,7,Fhorrifyingly bleak and, quite frankly,
OL,8,Fpretty scary at times, music is a safe
OL,9,Fhaven, a place to escape for so many,
OL,10,Fincluding myself.
OL,12,F"So tonight, I believe it's a powerful
OL,13,Fcelebration of incredible artists who
OL,14,Ffeel things deeply and intensely and
OL,15,Fwear their heart on their sleeve in
OL,16,Fmany different forms, all of which are
OL,17,Fprecious and should be protected at
OL,18,Fall costs.
OL,20,F"Thank you. I love you all so much."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU|D@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
