OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FRose and Bruno Mars won international
OL,7,Fsong of the year for APT, with the
OL,8,FBlackPink singer collecting the award.
OL,10,FShe said: "It is such an honour to be
OL,11,Freceiving this award in front of so
OL,12,Fmany talented and, you know, admirable
OL,13,Fmusicians here in the UK."
OL,15,FShe thanked Mars, saying: "Thank you
OL,16,Fso much for everything, for being my
OL,17,Fbiggest mentor and best friend. Love
OL,18,Fyou so much."
OL,26,@rD@KOUuD@ZO]wD@[OUzD@MO]
