OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FRapper Dave won the award for hip hop,
OL,7,Fgrime and rap act, while Fred Again..
OL,8,FSkepta and PlaqueBoyMax won the dance
OL,9,Fcategory, mysterious soul band Sault
OL,10,Fwon best R&B and Fender took home best
OL,11,Falternative act.
OL,13,FPerformances saw Robbie Williams front
OL,14,Fthe late Ozzy Osbourne's former band
OL,15,Fin a tribute to the Black Sabbath
OL,16,Fsinger and Harry Styles perform his
OL,17,Flatest single Aperture.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
