OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772532302
OL,3,COlivia Dean wins big at Brits as
OL,4,Cpolitical statements censored
OL,6,FOasis's Noel Gallagher was named
OL,7,Fsongwriter of the year, while record
OL,8,Fproducer and DJ Mark Ronson was
OL,9,Fhonoured with the outstanding
OL,10,Fcontribution to music award.
OL,12,FSinger-songwriter PinkPantheress, real
OL,13,Fname Victoria Walker, was named
OL,14,Fproducer of the year.
OL,16,FThe 24-year-old was the first woman
OL,17,Fand youngest ever artist to win the
OL,18,Faccolade, according to the Brit Awards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
